snippet.title: Andreas Carlund
snippet.description:
Officiell kanal för Andreas Carlund (författare) och Tidlös utbildning. Hemsidan är: http://tidlosutbildning.blogspot.se/

Official channel for Andreas Carlund (author) and Timeless Education. Look for "CC" next to video thumbnails for English subtitles. If the subs look weird then take a look at your settings. There will be some videos in English as well.
English language website: https://timeless-education.blogspot.com/
